Package: CopulaSCR
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Semi-competing Risks Data Using Copula-based Models
Version: 1.0
Author: Tonghui Yu 
Maintainer: Tonghui Yu <tonghui_yu@126.com>
Description: Simulate and analyze Semi-competing Risks Data using copula-based models. 
    The Semi-competing Risks Data consist of a terminal event time and single or multiple nonterminal event times. 
    The marginal survival functions of these event times are estimated nonparametrically.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.2),
    survival,
    foreach
Imports:
    quantreg (>= 5.97),
    acopula,
    copula (>= 1.1-3),
    doParallel (>= 1.0.17),
    prodlim (>= 2023.08.28),
    stats,
    BB (>=2019.10-1),
    graph (>= 1.80.0),
    Rgraphviz (>= 2.46.0),
    pracma,
    survminer,
    cowplot
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
